---
title: Summer Ratatouille with Fresh Tortelloni, Parmesan, and Basil
description: Ratatouille, a French peasant stew, is one of the first things our HelloFresh chefs learned to make in culinary school. Since then, it’s become one of their favorite recipes, with an infinite number of variations. This version includes fresh tortellini, making it hearty enough for dinner.
